---
---
<section class="relative pt-40 pb-48 bg-slate-900 clip-hero overflow-hidden">
    <img src="/assets/images/mujer.webp" alt="Consultoría Ejecutiva JMJ"
        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-top opacity-50 mix-blend-luminosity">

    <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[90%] md:w-[65%] h-full bg-jmj-blue/90 clip-accent z-10 backdrop-blur-[2px]">
    </div>
    <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 right-5 w-[45%] h-[50%] bg-jmj-orange/80 clip-slant z-10 mix-blend-multiply hidden md:block">
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex items-center h-full">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <h1 class="text-jmj-orange text-sm font-extrabold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-5 flex items-center gap-3 animate-fadeIn">
                <span class="w-10 h-0.5 bg-jmj-orange"></span>
                Gestión de Riesgos y Valor
            </h1>
            <p class="font-stix italic text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 font-medium opacity-0 translate-y-4 animate-fadeInUp">
                Transformamos la incertidumbre en resultados predecibles.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-200 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl font-light opacity-0 translate-y-4 animate-fadeInUp delay-200">
                Consultoría de ingeniería de élite especializada en reducción proactiva de riesgos, optimización de
                CAPEX y continuidad operativa.
            </p>
            <div class="opacity-0 translate-y-4 animate-fadeInUp delay-500">
                <a href="#contacto"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-jmj-orange text-white text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-[#d14b1c] transition-all shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(241,90,36,0.3)] hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Agendar Evaluación Estratégica
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
  .delay-200 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .delay-500 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
</style>
